<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥٤٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/734">أَصْبَغُ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3976">ابْنُ وَهْبٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7248">يُونُسَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">ابْنِ شِهَابٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2249">سَالِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">أَبِيهِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«سَمِعْتُ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: يُهِلُّ مُلَبِّدًا»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>